name: Sustainable living
description:
Growing up in the jungles of Papua New Guinea, I have always marvelled at how big an issue sustainability is. Growing up in a community in the Gulf Province, we loved spending time in nature, the feeling of wet grass and the warmth of the fire that we sat around late into the night telling stories. There was never a feeling of lack of anything.

Here is a little insight into how I grew up and how free it is. I hope you enjoy the story.
